Text: RE Yopst Well I volunteer to baby sit too And I dont live on the edge of the earth Although Im not up for the breastfeeding part hahaha Angie From Germany Chris Chris NRONcom To Angie Zeman out place which works out great We can go out for dinner pretty easy A lot of people dont seem to have that Judy said she would baby sit but its not worth the trip to the edge of the earth in Katy
